Enum MetricNamePostfixPolicy

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<MetricNamePostfixPolicy>
      • net.centro.rtb.monitoringcenter.config.MetricNamePostfixPolicy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<MetricNamePostfixPolicy>

    public enum MetricNamePostfixPolicy
extends Enum<MetricNamePostfixPolicy>
    Policy for enforcing a naming convention, where metric types are appended to metric names.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      ADD_ALL_TYPES
      Append the type of the metric to all metric names.
      ADD_COMPOSITE_TYPES
      Append the type of the metric only to names of composite metrics, such as timers, meters, and histograms.
      OFF
      Do not append the metric type to metric names.
